scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OFg2xCteqwKHsmjz-quKFA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afz-fxTA0GRGuUAwO45xA3Mq37mX2TBmGhEnbyhbFVAApQ&amp;oe=69CA1F95" alt="Slide 3 fra @thedesignersrepublic" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655227029_18571058416049614_6292579908013989602_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjE2MTg2MjQxMzIzOTgwNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjExNjl4MTU0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=dyZMfGD048AQ7kNvwEcZutr&amp;_nc_oc=AdrR8D4pp2Wk_Nfk4JnJELYZ6wBbGZx68uoISl_21X66i-byMGRo54EjoKPFPTqSUyc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OFg2xCteqwKHsmjz-quKFA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afz7kOv-N7hTNqWFJyWmOMAdGuc34c-JQUBdBw1xvo7hUA&amp;oe=69CA1683" alt="Slide 4 fra @thedesignersrepublic" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (4 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@thedesignersrepublic</strong></p><p>New TDR designed Seefeel SOL.HZ album cover featuring bespoke ‘Sfl(4e)’ logo built from (and corroded by) letterforms improvised as part the 6x26 un-gridded modular alphabets forming the basis for the TDRRunes project (potentially infinite WIP) exploring the parameters of legibility abstracting understanding beyond knowledge. <br/>
<br/>
TDRRunes is ultimately a plan to create user editable typographic digital artefacts for end-use anywhere and anyhow… but right now we’re having a fine time road testing being the end-users ourselves. This spells how we see Seefeel feeling… new beginnings in every memory… supernova sunsets...<br/>
<br/>
TDRRunes began as a way of spelling numbers, evolving from the TDRBingo NFT project. It might end up being something very different… it always does.<br/>
<br/>
#seefeel #typography #graphicdesign #recordcovers #glitch</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWD1ztGjA5R/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
